video_identification.title: Cultural Genocide in Palestine Gaza and Beyond | Prof. Munir Nuseibah

extracted_metadata.title: Cultural Genocide in Palestine Gaza and Beyond | Prof. Munir Nuseibah
extracted_metadata.description: Zochrot and TINAU hold a discussion with Prof. Munir Nuseibah to examine the Israeli attempts to conduct a cultural genocide in Palestine, focusing on the wide destruction of the Gaza Strip, but also showing other examples of cultural genocide elsewhere in Palestine. Language: English
